.The complete details including application form number with identity certificate copy containing date of submission of application form must be produced.Marriage registration certificate is an essential document.All the candidates must also produce a self declaration certificate that he / she has will not get any assistance from any other govt. dept. / board / nigam.Also Read \u2013 Haryana Mukhyamantri Mahila Shramik Samman Yojana3. Baccho Ki Shadi Par Vittiya Sahayata Yojana Haryana Eligibility CriteriaAll the candidates must fulfill the eligibility criteria as mentioned in the table below to avail assistance under Baccho Ki Shadi Par Vittiya Sahayata Yojana in Haryana:-Eligibility CriteriaMembership Years / \u0938\u0926\u0938\u094d\u092f\u0924\u093e \u0935\u0930\u094d\u09371 yearApply Frequency / \u0906\u0935\u0947\u0926\u0928 \u0915\u0940 \u0938\u0940\u092e\u093eupto 3 daughtersScheme For / \u0907\u0938 \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090fAllContinue After Death / \u092e\u0943\u0924\u094d\u092f\u0941 \u0915\u0947 \u092c\u093e\u0926 \u091c\u093e\u0930\u0940NoAll the registered labourers can now get Rs. 50,000 under Labour Welfare Board Marriage Assistance Scheme (\u092c\u091a\u094d\u091a\u094b\u0902 \u0915\u0940 \u0936\u093e\u0926\u0940 \u092a\u0930 \u0935\u093f\u0924\u094d\u0924\u0940\u092f \u0938\u0939\u093e\u092f\u0924\u093e (\u0938\u0941\u092a\u0941\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0940)) + Rs. 51,000 under Kanyadan Yojna (\u0915\u0928\u094d\u092f\u093e\u0926\u093e\u0928 \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e) = 1,01,000/-.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: hrylabour.gov.in  at  "}